rows.label: qst000401_msg0003
rows.name:
I want to play with them,
too, but I can't swim.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0004
rows.name:
So when everyone plays by the water,
I just stand here and stare.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0005
rows.name:
I want to practice swimming,
but I don't have the right
gear, so I'm stuck.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0006
rows.name:
There's a plant called
Buoyweed that grows by the
water at Coolley Lake.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0007
rows.name:
It floats really well, so I want
to use it for practice, but[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst000401_msg0008
rows.name:
there are monsters near where the
Buoyweed grows, so it's dangerous.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0009
rows.name:
The last time I went, I
almost got seriously hurt.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0011
rows.name:
I think about three of them
should be enough for practice.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0013
rows.name:
I saw some Buoyweed around the
middle of Coolley Lake last time.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0014
rows.name:
Let me know when you've
got three of them!
